{"tid":948522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【險陷冤獄】小巴司機與乘客爭執後被指非禮 官斥報假案少婦：心地非常唔好","createTime":"2018-12-20T06:46:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T03:01:57.000Z","uid":2748,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"966d09e3046256dbb93e6bdd55248bc6b8e0c682","tid":948522,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T06:46:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181220/large/1545283124_ae8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181220%2Flarge%2F1545283124_ae8d.jpg&h=d9341af2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n裁判官吳蕙芳(圓圖)(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n26歲少婦凌晨搭乘小巴，以100元紙幣付車資，事後卻聲稱自己支付了1,000元，要求司機找贖逾900元。雙方爭執下，少婦竟然報假案，自稱遭司機以手肘掃胸非禮。涉案少婦今在九龍城裁判法院認罪，主任裁判官吳蕙芳嚴斥她的誣告行徑卑劣、黑心，「你唔係有精神病，就係心地非常唔好」，並謂「人哋就可能無辜坐監，改變一生」。吳官先索取社會服務令報告，並將少婦還柙至下月3日判刑。少婦屈人不成，反令自己要於獄中過聖誕及元旦。<br />\n<br />\n育有兩名年幼子女的26歲女被告鄭凱婷，今早承認一項刑事恐嚇及三項誤導警務人員罪。她於庭上泣不成聲，兩度遭吳官提醒，要她平伏情緒。<br />\n<br />\n官：可能會搞到人哋妻離子散<br />\n吳官庭上指，女性指控男性非禮，會令對方難以反駁；一旦法庭相信女方指控，便會造成冤獄，「你仲要係影低情況下話人非禮你，心地差，根本就係擘大眼講大話」。吳官續指：「你就為咗人同你爭執，就要人坐監，你就心涼，你唔知坐監係好痛苦，人哋可能未犯過事，因為你黑心、誣告，搞到人哋妻離子散，冇咗份工，經濟拮据，鬱鬱不得志。」<br />\n<br />\n案情指今年6月5日凌晨2時許，被告於白加士街一輛小巴上與司機爭執。當時被告以100元支付16元車資，但堅稱自己付了兩張500元，要求對方多找贖900元。當時被告向司機稱：「你唔識我，我叫老公落嚟打你。」其後被告致電報警，分別向到場調查及錄口供的警員訛稱遭非禮。惟由於雙方均有用手機拍下爭執情況，警方翻看片段，證實並無非禮一事。被告警誡下承認因不滿司機態度而虛報非禮案。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：KCCC3422/18】"},{"pid":"ea9b3650d193560a45dc68fb3382e5736ea0946c","tid":948522,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":37,"score":-37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T06:47:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4402fadcb4508c2ca3847a93d2137bfc0173e9fc","tid":948522,"uid":223256,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"ea9b3650d193560a45dc68fb3382e5736ea0946c","tid":948522,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":37,"score":-37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T06:47:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T06:55:55.000Z","msg":"司機有咩錯"},{"pid":"1afeb09675247d80e3e94d33d1ddbf660e785952","tid":948522,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T06:56:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e24768e2d30dc15cd94dfed1efc415b363ae7e5","tid":948522,"uid":223256,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T06:58:24.000Z","msg":"當時被告以100元支付16元車資，但堅稱自己付了兩張500元，要求對方多找贖900元<br />\n<br />\n講大話都唔識講<br />\n比16元車資點會比兩張大牛<br />\non撚鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d63d3ad462b23e5f78c3bc8fe8c6468939745527","tid":948522,"uid":15872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e24768e2d30dc15cd94dfed1efc415b363ae7e5","tid":948522,"uid":223256,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T06:58:24.000Z","msg":"當時被告以100元支付16元車資，但堅稱自己付了兩張500元，要求對方多找贖900元<br />\n<br />\n講大話都唔識講<br />\n比16元車資點會比兩張大牛<br />\non撚鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T07:00:39.000Z","msg":"我都睇到一頭霧水<br />\n擺明屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d01dd5b0f7e610e7ebfc74ec267c54e535013e","tid":948522,"uid":194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d63d3ad462b23e5f78c3bc8fe8c6468939745527","tid":948522,"uid":15872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e24768e2d30dc15cd94dfed1efc415b363ae7e5","tid":948522,"uid":223256,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T06:58:24.000Z","msg":"當時被告以100元支付16元車資，但堅稱自己付了兩張500元，要求對方多找贖900元<br />\n<br />\n講大話都唔識講<br />\n比16元車資點會比兩張大牛<br />\non撚鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T07:00:39.000Z","msg":"我都睇到一頭霧水<br />\n擺明屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T07:03:43.000Z","msg":"條女應該真係有精神病"},{"pid":"11a755226391d19fecc6955e8ab66fdea3290404","tid":948522,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T07:10:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5febdc46f22881244a892a56391235c92a9ba8a","tid":948522,"uid":122867,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T07:19:45.000Z","msg":"正中抵撚死 鬼唔望坐完出返黎成頭家散鳩晒<br />\n再淪落到要做141 撞撚返個小巴師機俾佢砌鑊金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6549a10c393c8a54315ead332463448de34a38","tid":948522,"uid":122867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f5febdc46f22881244a892a56391235c92a9ba8a","tid":948522,"uid":122867,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T07:19:45.000Z","msg":"正中抵撚死 鬼唔望坐完出返黎成頭家散鳩晒<br />\n再淪落到要做141 撞撚返個小巴師機俾佢砌鑊金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T07:20:09.000Z","msg":"司"},{"pid":"8560cbc86bb625e8f0302897cfd9fe8787ca2c11","tid":948522,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T07:24:49.000Z","msg":"清官<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527d7af456ad0c3ba1b51129302ef9e78b7b9752","tid":948522,"uid":15,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T07:26:45.000Z","msg":"想俾1000千正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec447882b7918e50bbe8e117e2b6d9e134ca4b4","tid":948522,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T07:27:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71f77681b6cf2ea9db4e542fdd77ecda9b4f524","tid":948522,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T04:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b4da91eefec8b535c2f959cd89d6d6ddd0a928","tid":948522,"uid":76098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T05:13:00.000Z","msg":"果然係F.1最壞既女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ebb1d796015f8ab347fe3c88704601e5f72344c","tid":948522,"uid":69771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T15:55:35.000Z","msg":"兩個仔女有咁既老母"},{"pid":"6666a8c9428380dff1e229147cdcb496f94ace16","tid":948522,"uid":128603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T17:11:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2019-01-03</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">少婦誣告小巴司機非禮判緩刑 官勸勿再吸毒酗酒重新做人</span><br />\n<br />\n 少婦因車資找贖問題恐嚇小巴司機，要召來丈夫毆打對方，又聲稱遭非禮，警察原先拘捕司機，其後發現二人「對錄」片段發現查無此事，少婦早前於九龍城法院承認3項虛報有人犯罪，及1項刑事恐嚇。被告今沒有律師代表親自求情時一直啜泣，望法庭「畀多次機會」，遭主任裁判官痛斥「我要信你咩」指她案底累累，有傷人、吸毒、盜竊前科，最終判囚4個月，緩刑兩年。<br />\n      <br />\n      26歲被告鄭凱婷早前被還柙，聲稱「今次真係好有誠意會改」已幾個月未有飲酒又指自己已變好，吳官即言「幾個月啫，唔代表唔會變壞」又責被告不爭氣，「唔吸毒就飲酒」。是次被告自言因醉酒而犯事，但卻不知悔改，未能理解何以被捕而怪責社會，吳官指她已吸毒致自己「本末倒置、黑白不分」，即使已為人母仍從來無反省過自己。<br />\n      <br />\n      被告一直在犯人欄內邊哭邊求情，吳官不禁謂「你喊完未？喊無同情分㗎喺法庭！」除了多次勸被告不要再吸毒酗酒，又勸她要好好做人，為子女作好榜樣，望她可「醒醒定定，重新做人」，<span style=\"color: red;\">最後給予機會，暫不處理被告另一案緩刑案件，就本案判入獄4個月，緩刑兩年。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.stheadline.com/inews-content.php?cat=a&amp;nid=1564\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stheadline.com%2Finews-content.php%3Fcat%3Da%26nid%3D1564&d=oudMuPEce2JXF3%2FcKJezMozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=7e997d29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stheadline.com%2Finews-content.php%3Fcat%3Da%26nid%3D1564&h=8fb16186\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.stheadline.com/inews-content.php?cat=a&amp;nid=1564</a>"},{"pid":"81d19303a5df612b73014aae28bddc4d3e7f2768","tid":948522,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T03:01:57.000Z","msg":"咁都唔駛坐監，送佢入去俾人教訓下"}]}